{"word":"Ruth","slug":"ruth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ruth</b> <a href=\"#/H7327\">H7327</a> <br/> The daughter-in-law of Naomi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=4'>Rth 1:4</a><br/> Her devotion to Naomi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=18'>Rth 1:18</a><br/> Goes to Bethlehem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=19'>Rth 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=22'>Rth 1:22</a><br/> Gleaned in the field of Boaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=3'>Rth 2:3</a><br/> Receives kindness from Boaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=17'>Rth 2:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=3&verse=15'>Rth 3:15</a><br/> Under Naomi's instructions claims from Boaz the duty of a kinsman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=3&verse=9'>Rth 3:9</a><br/> Marries Boaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=13'>Rth 4:13</a><br/> Becomes an ancestor of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=13'>Rth 4:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=22'>Rth 4:22</a>"}]}